public Generator<? extends PageElement> getGenerator(CmsRequest<? extends PageElement> request)
        Description copied from interface: PageElement
        Get a generator instance for the specified content type. This method will be called once per request by CMS internals. This is not intended to be used by ContentElement/Generator implementors.
        Parameters:
        request - the request.
        Returns:
        the generator. Return null to indicate that a generator isn't supported for the specified request.
